Challenge2:
Fetching data in React based on user input (onChange)
Creatte a textbox that will call the followng api that is fetching data from the JSON Server APIs.
"https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users"
use onchange event handler to be called when a name is type in a textbox and display it on browser
NOTTE:
Displaying Loading state when fetching data from API in React
It is always a good practice. display a loading message (or a spinner) by making use of a local state.
Handle error whle fetchng data from the server

